METHOD FOR DATA EXTRACTION::
I used my own simple methodology which I call it the "Trunk-Branch-Leaf method" or the "TREE Method".

TREE METHOD//TRUNK-BRANCH-LEAF METHOD:
1. Firstly, I noted down all the major topics of research done up to the date of summer 2025. (TRUNK)
2. Secondly, I then noted down the sub-topics within these major topics of the research noted down. (BRANCH)
3. Finally, I extracted data of each and every subtopic in an order from one to another in a manner. (LEAF)
.........................................................................................................................................................................
METHOD FOR DATA VERIFICATION::
I simply used my own created DV method, known as, "PDVCO Method" or the "PURE DATA-VERIFICATION-and-CALCULATION-in-ORDER method".

PDVCO METHOD//PURE DATA-VERIFICATION-and-CALCULATION-in-ORDER METHOD:
1. Firstly, I would search trusted sources of information like one example is "www.wikepedia.com" for each and every minor topic in order. (SEARCH).
2. Secondly, I would check all the data I have collected manually by searching all the trusted sources of information for each and every subtopic in order.(VERIFICATION). 
3. Finally, I would calculate the percentage of pure data present in the data which I collected by using TREE Method on CHATGPT 4. (CALCULATION).
